  m_text: "B-prepared is a European disaster preparedness ecosystem that uses immersive
    tools\u2014including a disaster knowledge platform, \"Disastropedia,\" and VR
    training\u2014to foster a culture of community resilience, security research,
    and crisis awareness. It helps people understand alerts, act during emergencies,
    and follow instructions using realistic historical scenarios."
